{
  "stem": "13817.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The barracks were three tiers, just wooden planks you would lay on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You had about a foot, a foot and a half to lay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And during the day, you would be put out in the exercise yard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And all you would do is run around, hop like a frog, or-- or roll around, just to keep you busy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In one corner of the exercise yard was a pile of rocks, of heavy rocks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They would tell you to carry it to the next corner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So for-- for about 8 to 10 days in this quarantine, all you do is just being harassed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the food in there was-- the-- these kapos would steal half of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You would get half of the ration, which was already small to start with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this was a ongoing thing for about like I said 8 to 10 days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "After that we were loaded, all of a sudden loaded--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the brutality-- one of the cruel-- cruelest scene, one of them that I saw was when we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other transport, like I said, there were men, women, and children coming from-- from Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, when they separated the men and the women and the children, there was one man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He went over and wanted to kiss his wife goodbye and hold his baby for-- a child of about a year, year and a half, would hold her for a little while.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the Nazis says you don't have-- give that child back to your wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he gave it back, he went over and wanted to kiss-- kiss this baby.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
